60&h=540&q=80&fm=webp 960w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/r6xJ4nmPZXAiy0ToL2Hr7/c732959270c87c6c445e463c0e2a68b4/How_to_buy_crypto_with_MetaMask.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=webp 1920w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/r6xJ4nmPZXAiy0ToL2Hr7/c732959270c87c6c445e463c0e2a68b4/How_to_buy_crypto_with_MetaMask.png?w=3840&h=2160&q=80&fm=webp 3840w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw","type":"image/webp"}],"fallback":{"src":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/r6xJ4nmPZXAiy0ToL2Hr7/c732959270c87c6c445e463c0e2a68b4/How_to_buy_crypto_with_MetaMask.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=png","srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/r6xJ4nmPZXAiy0ToL2Hr7/c732959270c87c6c445e463c0e2a68b4/How_to_buy_crypto_with_MetaMask.png?w=480&h=270&q=80&fm=png 480w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/r6xJ4nmPZXAiy0ToL2Hr7/c732959270c87c6c445e463c0e2a68b4/How_to_buy_crypto_with_MetaMask.png?w=960&h=540&q=80&fm=png 960w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/r6xJ4nmPZXAiy0ToL2Hr7/c732959270c87c6c445e463c0e2a68b4/How_to_buy_crypto_with_MetaMask.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=png 1920w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/r6xJ4nmPZXAiy0ToL2Hr7/c732959270c87c6c445e463c0e2a68b4/How_to_buy_crypto_with_MetaMask.png?w=3840&h=2160&q=80&fm=png 3840w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"}},"layout":"constrained","width":1920,"height":1080}},"publishDate":"November 4, 2024","authors":[{"name":"MetaMask","createProfilePage":null,"profileUrl":"metamask"}],"content":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Wondering how to buy crypto, but not sure where to start? You’ve come to the right place. Buying crypto with MetaMask is swift, seamless, and safe. You can use methods like a credit card, debit card, bank account, Apple Pay, Google Pay, or PayPal. No need for centralized exchanges. We’ve cut out all of the unnecessary steps — saving you time, and money on excess fees too.</p>\n<p>Below, we'll give you an overview of how we make MetaMask wallet powerful, secure, and configurable when you buy cryptocurrencies. Then, you'll find videos and step-by-step guides showing you exactly how to buy crypto with MetaMask on your browser or mobile app.</p>\n<p>Let's get into it! 🦊</p>\n<h3>How MetaMask empowers you when buying crypto</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Buy crypto straight into your MetaMask wallet.</li>\n<li>Choose the best quote from our industry-leading aggregator.</li>\n<li>Avoid centralized exchanges, extra steps, and additional costs.</li>\n<li>Use MetaMask wallet in 188 countries with over 80 currencies available.</li>\n<li>Select from hundreds of your favorite tokens across 15+ networks including: Ethereum, Linea, Optimism, BNB Chain, Polygon, zkSync, Base, Arbitrum, and Avalanche.</li>\n<li>Go from cash to crypto back to cash. All <a href=\"https://portfolio.metamask.io/\">in one place</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How MetaMask wallet keeps you secure when buying crypto</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Get 24/7 help whenever you need it from our expert customer service team.</li>\n<li>We only work with trusted providers, ensuring that they comply with applicable regulations and are legitimate, responsible parties.</li>\n<li>Preserving your privacy is paramount: MetaMask does not store — nor do we have access to — any personal information you provide when buying or selling crypto, such as payment details, personal data, or email addresses.</li>\n<li>Unlike a centralized exchange, neither MetaMask nor our partners have access to the cryptocurrencies after you purchase or transfer them, meaning you can access your assets immediately without a holding period.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How MetaMask wallet gives you choice buying crypto</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Choose your preferred way to buy crypto using: debit card, credit card, bank transfer, instant ACH, PayPal, Apple Pay, Google Pay, Ideal, SEPA bank transfers, and alternative local payment methods. These are subject to availability based on your region.</li>\n<li>Select your preferred quote and provider.</li>\n<li>You can buy crypto using MetaMask Portfolio on desktop or the MetaMask app on mobile.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>If you’re using MetaMask Extension:</h3>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OtoymxLYQYU?si=dn_Ly9FIv0pXRbex\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p>Clicking the <strong>Buy &#x26; Sell</strong> button on the MetaMask extension will redirect you to <a href=\"https://portfolio.metamask.io/\">MetaMask Portfolio</a>. Once there, connect your MetaMask wallet.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Click <strong>Move crypto</strong></li>\n<li>Click <strong>Buy.</strong></li>\n<li>Select your region, and currency — located to the right of your wallet address.</li>\n<li>Select payment method.</li>\n<li>Select the token and network you want to purchase on. Example: ETH on Ethereum.</li>\n<li>Enter the amount desired in your local currency. Example: $100 of ETH.</li>\n<li>Select the best real-time quote from our industry-leading providers.</li>\n<li>You'll be securely redirected to the provider's website to complete the purchase, and funds will be deposited in your MetaMask wallet.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Success! 🦊</p>\n<h3>If you’re using the MetaMask mobile app:</h3>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vtjp3w8wSEg?si=bn1CSHjvj9nGkwag\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<ol>\n<li>Sign-in to your MetaMask app.</li>\n<li>Tap the menu button, which has two arrows in opposite directions and is located on the bottom of your homepage screen.</li>\n<li>Tap <strong>Buy</strong></li>\n<li>Select your region and currency—this is located to the right of your wallet address.</li>\n<li>Select the crypto token and network that you want to buy. Example: ETH on Ethereum.</li>\n<li>Enter the crypto amount you want to buy. Example: 0.5 ETH.</li>\n<li>Select the payment method you want to use to buy crypto. Example: debit card, credit card, bank account, or PayPal balance. Availability will depend on your region.</li>\n<li>Tap <strong>Get quotes</strong> to proceed. Select the best quote from our industry-leading providers.</li>\n<li>Complete the transaction on the provider’s portal, and link your desired payment method.</li>\n<li>Review the order summary in your MetaMask app, and confirm the transaction to get crypto in your wallet.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Success! 🦊</p>\n<p><strong>Ready to get started? If you’re on desktop, download <a href=\"https://metamask.io/download/\">MetaMask Extension</a>. If you’re on mobile, <a href=\"https://metamask.io/download/\">download the MetaMask app</a> for iOS or Android.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Need more help? We got you. Head to <a href=\"https://support.metamask.io/metamask-portfolio/move-crypto/sell/how-to-sell-your-crypto-assets-for-fiat-currency-in-metamask/?utm_source=owned-metamask&#x26;utm_medium=content&#x26;utm_campaign=cmp-7654441-afbf08\">MetaMask Support</a> to speak with our team of experts around-the-clock.</strong></p>"}},"categories":[{"contentful_id":"3tE0tpmPMGsXezpOhKyWGO","node_locale":"ja","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNewsCategory"},"name":"最新","slug":"latest"}],"metaTitle":"How to buy crypto ","metaDescription":"Explore the ways to buy crypto directly using your debit card, credit card, PayPal, and bank account with MetaMask wallet. ","canonicalUrl":null,"isPrivate":false},{"contentful_id":"5xrrnYrndv1oQHew8nvh2H","node_locale":"ja","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNews"},"title":"MetaMaskで仮想通貨を売却して現金化する方法","slug":"how-to-sell-crypto-for-cash","subtitle":"MetaMask Portfolioの売却機能を使用すると、審査済みのプロバイダーを通じて数回のクリックで仮想通貨を売却し、現金化できます。","image":{"title":"ja - sell","description":"","file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/fv9yIqYdgRNAvtQ0P8HpY/8dbb965f0c36bbf2c41d555c601cc1fe/ja_-_sell.png"},"gatsbyImageData":{"images":{"sources":[{"srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/fv9yIqYdgRNAvtQ0P8HpY/8dbb965f0c36bbf2c41d555c601cc1fe/ja_-_sell.png?w=480&h=270&q=80&fm=webp 480w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/fv9yIqYdgRNAvtQ0P8HpY/8dbb965f0c36bbf2c41d555c601cc1fe/ja_-_sell.png?w=960&h=540&q=80&fm=webp 960w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/fv9yIqYdgRNAvtQ0P8HpY/8dbb965f0c36bbf2c41d555c601cc1fe/ja_-_sell.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=webp 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw","type":"image/webp"}],"fallback":{"src":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/fv9yIqYdgRNAvtQ0P8HpY/8dbb965f0c36bbf2c41d555c601cc1fe/ja_-_sell.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=png","srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/fv9yIqYdgRNAvtQ0P8HpY/8dbb965f0c36bbf2c41d555c601cc1fe/ja_-_sell.png?w=480&h=270&q=80&fm=png 480w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/fv9yIqYdgRNAvtQ0P8HpY/8dbb965f0c36bbf2c41d555c601cc1fe/ja_-_sell.png?w=960&h=540&q=80&fm=png 960w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/fv9yIqYdgRNAvtQ0P8HpY/8dbb965f0c36bbf2c41d555c601cc1fe/ja_-_sell.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=png 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"}},"layout":"constrained","width":1920,"height":1080}},"publishDate":"November 4, 2024","authors":[{"name":"MetaMask","createProfilePage":null,"profileUrl":"metamask"}],"content":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>MetaMask Portfolioの売却機能を使用すると、暗号資産を法定通貨 (USD、EUR、GBP) で簡単に出金できます。 購入機能と組み合わせることで、自己完結型のweb3エクスペリエンスが完成します。必要な仲介サービスが減り、<strong>銀行口座やPayPal</strong> など対応している送金先を指定して、より短時間で法定通貨を直接受け取れます。</p>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IDoCq5vKCBQ?si=ofiUAMWgzE36qya3\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<br/> \n<h3>審査済みの仮想通貨プロバイダー</h3>\n<br/> \n<p>MetaMaskは1社のプロバイダーに限ることなく、何社もの審査済みのプロバイダーをご用意しています。その多くは<a href=\"http://portfolio.metamask.io/buy?utm_source=metamask&#x26;utm_medium=blog&#x26;utm_campaign=feature-articles_content\">購入</a>フローと同じプロバイダーで、当社の高い基準を満たしており、イーサリアムメインネットのETHをご希望の対応法定通貨にリアルタイムで変換できるよう、さまざまなオプションを提供しています。</p>\n<h3>世界中が対象</h3>\n<br/> \n<p>売却機能は現在米国 <em>(州による制限が適用されます)</em>、英国、ヨーロッパの一部でご利用いただけますが、世界中のコミュニティでご利用いただけるよう今後他の地域に拡大される予定です。 ユーザーが仮想通貨の世界に自由に出入りできる手段を提供することが重要であり、これらのオプションにより、さらに多くの人々が<a href=\"https://learn.metamask.io/lessons/what-is-web3\">web3</a>を手軽に利用できるようになることを願っております。 まずはイーサリアムメインネットのETHのサポートから開始し、間もなくレイヤー2ネットワークのネイティブガストークンと、USD、EUR、GBPの法定通貨に拡張される予定です。</p>\n<h3>MetaMask Portfolioで仮想通貨売却機能を使用する方法</h3>\n<br/> \n<p>仮想通貨を売って現金化する方法</p>\n<ol>\n<li>MetaMaskウォレットを「<a href=\"http://portfolio.metamask.io?utm_source=metamask&#x26;utm_medium=blog&#x26;utm_campaign=feature_articles_content\">portfolio.metamask.io</a>」に接続します。</li>\n<li>「<a href=\"http://portfolio.metamask.io/sell?utm_source=metamask&#x26;utm_medium=blog&#x26;utm_campaign=feature_articles_content\">売却</a>」タブをクリックして開始します。</li>\n<li>地域を選択します。</li>\n<li>売却する仮想通貨トークンとネットワークを選択します (例: イーサリアムのETH)。</li>\n<li>お住まいの地域で利用可能な法定通貨の口座を選択します (銀行口座、PayPalなど)。</li>\n<li>売却する仮想通貨の数量を入力します (例: 0.5 ETH)。</li>\n<li>利用可能なさまざまなプロバイダーのクォートがすべてリアルタイムで表示されます。 1つ選択して続行します。</li>\n<li>プロバイダーのWebサイトにリダイレクトされるので、法定通貨の口座に登録してリンクさせます。その後は、自動的にMetaMask Portfolioに戻ります。</li>\n<li>「ETHを[Provider]に送金」を選択し、ウォレットから法定通貨の口座に仮想通貨を送金します。</li>\n<li>MetaMaskウォレットでトランザクションを確定させます。</li>\n<li>「売却」タブで注文の処理状況を確認できます。 所要時間はプロバイダーによって異なり、資金が法定通貨の口座に反映されるまで数日かかる場合があります。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>以上で、現金化は完了です！ 🦊</p>\n<h3>プロバイダーを整理</h3>\n<br/> \n<p>MetaMask Portfolioの購入および売却機能を使うと、仮想通貨と法定通貨の双方向の取引が可能で、プロバイダーの多くは購入と売却で共通です。 そのため、特定のプロバイダー1社で登録と銀行口座のリンクを一度行うだけで済みます。 ぜひ、これらの機能をご活用いただけることを願っております。</p>\n<p>始める準備はいいですか？ 詳細は、<a href=\"https://metamask.io/portfolio/?utm_source=metamask&#x26;utm_medium=blog&#x26;utm_campaign=feature-articles_content\">metamask.io/portfolio/</a>をご覧ください。</p>\n<p><em><strong>MetaMask Portfolio: web3のすべてを把握して管理</strong></em></p>\n<p><em>MetaMask Portfolioは、包括的かつユーザーフレンドリーなプラットフォームを提供し、ユーザーのweb3のニーズを満たすと同時に、思い通りのコントロールを可能にします。 ダッシュボード、購入、スワップ、ブリッジ、ステーキングなど、あらゆる機能が揃っています。 当社は常に有意義なアップデートを通じて、DAppの改善と進化に取り組んでいます。 <a href=\"https://metamask.io/portfolio/?utm_source=metamask&#x26;utm_medium=blog&#x26;utm_campaign=feature-articles_content\">こちら</a>をクリックして、MetaMask Portfolioとその機能の詳細をご覧ください。</em></p>"}},"categories":[{"contentful_id":"3tE0tpmPMGsXezpOhKyWGO","node_locale":"ja","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNewsCategory"},"name":"最新","slug":"latest"}],"metaTitle":"MetaMaskで仮想通貨を売却して現金化する方法","metaDescription":"MetaMaskの売却機能で仮想通貨を売って現金化し、厳選されたプロバイダーで暗号資産を法定通貨に容易に変換する方法を説明します。それでは始めましょう。","canonicalUrl":"https://support.metamask.io/metamask-portfolio/move-crypto/sell/how-to-sell-your-crypto-assets-for-fiat-currency-in-metamask/","isPrivate":false},{"contentful_id":"1ZwT5dKh4Z0FZuaBp7YSPK","node_locale":"ja","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNews"},"title":"Transfers from Coinbase and Binance now available in MetaMask","slug":"metamask-centralized-exchange-transfers-coinbase-binance","subtitle":"MetaMask launches new CEX transfer feature to make your wallet more powerful. ","image":{"title":"Centralized exchange transfers MetaMask now available","description":"Centralized exchange transfers from Coinbase and Binance now available on MetaMask. ","file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/52F4XvZIuxDaSK5SF6bWwJ/c27acb9c9709a0c5e04a590ad46e2b71/Centralized_exchange_transfers_MetaMask_now_availabe.png"},"gatsbyImageData":{"images":{"sources":[{"srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/52F4XvZIuxDaSK5SF6bWwJ/c27acb9c9709a0c5e04a590ad46e2b71/Centralized_exchange_transfers_MetaMask_now_availabe.png?w=480&h=270&q=80&fm=webp 480w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/52F4XvZIuxDaSK5SF6bWwJ/c27acb9c9709a0c5e04a590ad46e2b71/Centralized_exchange_transfers_MetaMask_now_availabe.png?w=960&h=540&q=80&fm=webp 960w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/52F4XvZIuxDaSK5SF6bWwJ/c27acb9c9709a0c5e04a590ad46e2b71/Centralized_exchange_transfers_MetaMask_now_availabe.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=webp 1920w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/52F4XvZIuxDaSK5SF6bWwJ/c27acb9c9709a0c5e04a590ad46e2b71/Centralized_exchange_transfers_MetaMask_now_availabe.png?w=3840&h=2160&q=80&fm=webp 3840w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw","type":"image/webp"}],"fallback":{"src":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/52F4XvZIuxDaSK5SF6bWwJ/c27acb9c9709a0c5e04a590ad46e2b71/Centralized_exchange_transfers_MetaMask_now_availabe.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=png","srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/52F4XvZIuxDaSK5SF6bWwJ/c27acb9c9709a0c5e04a590ad46e2b71/Centralized_exchange_transfers_MetaMask_now_availabe.png?w=480&h=270&q=80&fm=png 480w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/52F4XvZIuxDaSK5SF6bWwJ/c27acb9c9709a0c5e04a590ad46e2b71/Centralized_exchange_transfers_MetaMask_now_availabe.png?w=960&h=540&q=80&fm=png 960w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/52F4XvZIuxDaSK5SF6bWwJ/c27acb9c9709a0c5e04a590ad46e2b71/Centralized_exchange_transfers_MetaMask_now_availabe.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=png 1920w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/52F4XvZIuxDaSK5SF6bWwJ/c27acb9c9709a0c5e04a590ad46e2b71/Centralized_exchange_transfers_MetaMask_now_availabe.png?w=3840&h=2160&q=80&fm=png 3840w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"}},"layout":"constrained","width":1920,"height":1080}},"publishDate":"October 30, 2024","authors":[{"name":"Clarissa Watson","createProfilePage":true,"profileUrl":"clarissa-watson"}],"content":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>MetaMask Portfolio now supports centralized exchange (CEX) transfers from Coinbase and Binance, streamlining the process of transferring assets to your crypto wallet.</p>\n<p>Many web3 users have digital assets divided across multiple wallets and accounts, creating a fragmented experience. Moving assets from one platform to another can be overly complicated and involve many steps—fraught with the risks of copying and pasting addresses incorrectly, and potential security concerns. MetaMask’s new CEX transfer feature is a solution to this issue, making your wallet more powerful, while also strengthening security.</p>\n<p><strong>Instant transfer of assets from centralized exchanges into your MetaMask wallet</strong></p>\n<p>MetaMask CEX transfers allow you to immediately move assets between accounts, eliminating the need for manually entering addresses. And, if you have bank accounts linked to your Coinbase or Binance accounts, purchasing crypto directly with your bank account to your MetaMask wallet has never been easier. No additional KYC necessary.</p>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/z_wNpeCZubE?si=Ab5IgUTkcxL73JNY\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p>In April 2024, MetaMask partnered with <a href=\"https://metamask.io/news/latest/metamask-partners-with-meld-to-scale-crypto-adoption/?utm_source=owned-metamask&#x26;utm_medium=content&#x26;utm_campaign=cmp-7313062-afbf08\">Meld</a> and <a href=\"https://www.meshconnect.com/blog/mesh-and-metamask-revolutionizing-digital-asset-management-through-innovation\">Mesh</a> to launch a feature that allowed users to <a href=\"https://metamask.io/news/latest/track-your-crypto-exchange-and-wallet-balances/?utm_source=owned-metamask&#x26;utm_medium=content&#x26;utm_campaign=cmp-7323064-afbf08\">track external CEX balances</a> by linking Coinbase or Binance accounts directly from the <a href=\"https://portfolio.metamask.io/?utm_source=owned-metamask&#x26;utm_medium=content&#x26;utm_campaign=cmp-7333067-afbf08\">MetaMask Portfolio</a> dashboard. Now, you can view CEX balances, and also transfer assets from these exchanges into your MetaMask wallet. Neither MetaMask, nor our partners in this integration, will ever have access to your exchange login credentials, or share your wallet addresses with third parties.</p>\n<p>CEX transfers will initially support Coinbase or Binance accounts, with expansion to additional exchanges on the horizon. No fees will be charged when transferring digital assets from exchanges to MetaMask. A nominal transaction fee of 0.25% will be applied when transferring from MetaMask to centralized exchanges. Network gas fees also apply.</p>\n<p><strong>By bridging the gap between self-custodial and centralized platforms, MetaMask is paving the way for a more powerful, integrated, and user-friendly DeFi ecosystem. Head to <a href=\"https://portfolio.metamask.io/?utm_source=owned-metamask&#x26;utm_medium=content&#x26;utm_campaign=cmp-7333067-afbf08\">MetaMask Portfolio</a> today to get started with CEX transfers.</strong></p>"}},"categories":[{"contentful_id":"3tE0tpmPMGsXezpOhKyWGO","node_locale":"ja","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNewsCategory"},"name":"最新","slug":"latest"}],"metaTitle":null,"metaDescription":"MetaMask launches new CEX transfer feature to make your wallet more powerful. ","canonicalUrl":null,"isPrivate":false}]},"footer":{"contentful_id":"75bFgEllkMxpVsY8wWlroX","node_locale":"ja","internal":{"type":"ContentfulLayoutFooter"},"logo":{"contentful_id":"6fkPzzTMo3IoMKGMshuSVD","node_locale":"ja","internal":{"type":"ContentfulLogo"},"title":"MetaMask Logo","logo":{"title":"mm-logo","description":"","file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/4zJfzJbG3kTDSk5Wo4RJI1/1b363263141cf629b28155e2625b56c9/mm-logo.svg"},"gatsbyImageData":null},"logoDarkMode":{"title":"mm-logo-white","description":"","file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/2qy1wS5MmZOXkXn9yFlGJp/f3797a512c283e6f71450abd408b7452/mm-logo-white.svg"},"gatsbyImageData":null},"link":"/","newTab":false,"displayTitle":false,"wi